; https://github.com/tldr-pages/tldr/blob/master/pages/common/openclaw-doctor.md

% openclaw-doctor, common

# Run diagnostics
openclaw doctor

# Run diagnostics with automatic fixes
openclaw doctor --fix

# Run diagnostics non-interactively
openclaw doctor --non-interactive

# Display help
openclaw doctor <__h___help_>
